    "Precision is defined as the fraction of TP out of all expected positives (TP + FP).",
    "Recall, on the other hand, assesses the fraction of TP out of all real positives (TP + FN) and is defined as:",
    "The F1 score, which ranges from 0 to 1, is the harmonic mean of accuracy and recall.",
    "The F1 score is a well-balanced measure of accuracy and memory.",
    "Mathematically, it is as follows:"
  ]
